title: NHL suspends Stars' Demers two games for elbowing Penguins' Bonino
text:
Published By: Pittsburgh Post: Penguins - Today 
Dallas Stars defenseman Jason Demers was suspended two games by the NHL for elbowing Penguins center Nick Bonino in the face....
